response.overview: Toni Fitzgerald is a stand-up comic. The only issue is she isn't funny. Not to her workmates, not to her roommate, not even to her Mum. So when she stumbles upon a cult that doesn't approve of popular culture, she's offered an opportunity that she can't refuse. Toni pretends that the most famous lines of comedy history are her original stand-up. But how long will it be until they find out, and how far will Toni go to remain the funniest person in the room?
response.title: Toni Fitzgerald's Cult Following
